about that.

00:42:19.280 --> 00:42:21.280
And they're just driving me so
nuts that I'm actually sitting

00:42:21.280 --> 00:42:23.650
here thinking, OK, now you've
made it where I no longer want

00:42:23.650 --> 00:42:25.920
to interact with you because
there's no preference setting

00:42:25.920 --> 00:42:27.890
I could do to turn that
little sucker off.

00:42:27.890 --> 00:42:29.380
They're making it possible
for someone else

00:42:29.380 --> 00:42:30.840
to enter the space.

00:42:30.840 --> 00:42:33.350
Think about what you're doing
is managing attention.

00:42:33.350 --> 00:42:34.980
And then think about in
