00:42:43.140 --> 00:42:44.890
They've changed the
currency exchange.

00:42:44.890 --> 00:42:47.340
So I think that becomes a really
interesting metric as

00:42:47.340 --> 00:42:51.010
we go forward, how
to look at that.

